"Determine the Coefficient of Lift value for an aircraft flying straight and level at the given airspeed, using the provided data:\n \nMass:\t1 100 kg\nTAS:\t200 kt\nDensity:\t1.225 kg/m3\nWing area:\t13.5 m2\nG:\t9.8 m/s2": "0.123",
"Consider a multi-engined commercial jet with underslung wing-mounted engines flying at the stall speed with idle power. If power is increased, CLMAX will (1) ___ and the stall speed will (2) ___.\n\n>>> A) (1) remain the same; (2) decrease": "(1) remain the same; (2) decrease",
"Regarding a symmetrical aerofoil section, which statement is correct?\n\nThe lift coefficient...\n\n>>> A) equals zero when the angle of attack is zero.": "equals zero when the angle of attack is zero.",
