"Lift is a function of:": "velocity, wing planform area, CL and density.",
"An aircraft is cruising at an airspeed of 295 kt with a lift coefficient (CL) of 0.6. Following turbulence, the pilot reduces the speed to 250 kt. What is the new value of CL?": "0.84",
