"If the lift generated by a given wing is 1 000 kN, what will be the lift if the wing area is doubled?\n\n>>> A) 2 000 kN": "2 000 kN",
"Which of the following statements about positively cambered airfoils is correct?\n\n>>> A) The angle of attack will have a negative value when the lift coefficient equals zero.": "The angle of attack will have a negative value when the lift coefficient equals zero.",
"Refer to figure 081-40.\nWhich of the following statements is correct?\n\n>>> A) Line 2 corresponds to aerofoil 4": "Line 2 corresponds to aerofoil 4",
