"Calculate the VA for an aerobatic aeroplane with a VS0 of 110 kt and a VS1 of 123 kt.": "301 kt",
"Determine the VA for an aerobatic airplane given a stall speed VS0 of 43 kt and a stall speed VS1 of 59 kt.\n\n>>> A) 145 kt": "145 kt",
