"Which of these statements concerning flight in turbulence is correct?": "VB is the design speed for maximum gust intensity.",
"Refer to an aircraft in an unaccelerated straight and level flight with a lift coefficient (CL) of 0.35, and consider that a change in 1° of angle of attack (AoA) changes the CL by 0.079. Therefore, a vertical gust that increases the angle of attack by 2°, leads to a load factor of:": "1.45",
