"Propeller efficiency is:\n\n>>> A) the ratio of power available (Thrust × TAS) to shaft power (Torque × RPM).": "the ratio of power available (Thrust × TAS) to shaft power (Torque × RPM).",
"How do the (1) blade angle and (2) angle of attack change for a constant speed propeller when IAS increases?": "(1) varies; (2) remains constant",
"Which statement correctly describes the impact of icing on a propeller?": "Icing can cause a reduction of 20% of thrust in the inner part of the propeller blade.",
