"According to CS-25, how is the minimum control speed (VMC) determined by the manufacturer?": "At a speed not exceeding 1.13 Vs1 in the take-off configuration.",
"Which situation has the most adverse effect on controllability with one engine out?": "Empty aircraft during go-around.",
